 "Create the case story. A good case is one \nthat describes a controversy or sets the scene by describing the characters \ninvolved and the situation. It should also allow for some action to be taken \nin order to gain resolution of the situation.": "Itt \u00edrja le az esett\u00f6rt\u00e9netet! A j\u00f3 eset egy probl\u00e9m\u00e1t, \nhelysz\u00ednt, egy karaktert, egy bonyolult szitu\u00e1ci\u00f3t \u00edr le. \nAz esetle\u00edr\u00e1st azzal a c\u00e9llal tessz\u00fck k\u00f6zz\u00e9, hogy a megfelel\u0151 \nelj\u00e1r\u00e1s kialak\u00edt\u00e1s\u00e1t el\u0151seg\u00edts\u00fck.", 
